Corporate Security Policy Document
=================================

SECTION 1: ACCESS CONTROL
All file shares must implement proper authentication.
Guest access should be limited to public resources only.

SECTION 2: DATA CLASSIFICATION
- PUBLIC: General company information
- INTERNAL: Employee access required
- CONFIDENTIAL: Department specific access
- RESTRICTED: Executive/HR access only

SECTION 3: LEGACY SYSTEMS
Departments maintaining legacy systems must:
1. Document encryption methods
2. Maintain access logs
3. Schedule regular security audits

Violations of this policy may result in disciplinary action.

Document Version: 2.1
Effective Date: January 1, 2024